{"id":329941,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/01/nbspnbspnbsp/","date":"2014-01-16T05:32:46Z","modified":"2014-01-16T05:32:46Z","title":"&#20911;&#23398;&#33635; | &#20911;&#23398;&#33635;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;*&#24494;&#35821;&#24405;*&amp;nbsp;&#65288;&#19968;&#65289;","content":"<p><p align=\"center\">\n<span>冯</span><span>学荣</span><span> <br />\n*</span><span>微语录</span><span>*<br />\n<span>（一）</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n“甲午海</span><span>战</span><span>的失</span><span>败</span><span>，</span><span>标</span><span>志着洋</span><span>务</span><span>运</span><span>动</span><span>的失</span><span>败</span><span>”，</span><span>这</span><span>是最愚民的教育之一，因</span><span>为</span><span>如果依照</span><span>这</span><span>个</span><span>逻辑</span><span>，拿李阳的英</span><span>语</span><span>跟一个新加坡</span><span>华</span><span>人的英</span><span>语</span><span>比，</span><span>发现</span><span>李阳</span><span>输</span><span>了，得出：李阳的英</span><span>语</span><span>教育很失</span><span>败</span><span>。或者拿当今中国海</span><span>军</span><span>和美国海</span><span>军</span><span>相比，</span><span>输了，</span><span>然后得出：中国改革开放事</span><span>业</span><span>是失</span><span>败</span><span>的。大</span><span>陆</span><span>的孩子接受</span><span>这样</span><span>混乱</span><span>的</span><span>逻辑</span><span>教育，怎么会不蠢？</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n中国人从近代史中最</span><span>应该</span><span>吸取的</span><span>经验</span><span>是：内政外交一定要跳出意</span><span>识</span><span>形</span><span>态</span><span>的</span><span>牵绊</span><span>，遵照“利益最大化”的</span><span>铁</span><span>律做决策，</span><span>这样</span><span>才算老成</span><span>谋</span><span>国，才能</span><span>为</span><span>国家民族、</span><span>为</span><span>老百姓</span><span>谋</span><span>取最大的</span><span>实际</span><span>利益。一切政治都是利益，只要</span><span>获</span><span>利最大，一切政治</span><span>问题</span><span>都可以商量，没有不可商量的政治，没有任何</span><span>主义和节操，</span><span>能比老百姓的切身利益更重要。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n“弱国无外交”的</span><span>说</span><span>法是无</span><span>视</span><span>外交的价</span><span>值</span><span>。它无法解</span><span>释</span><span>日俄</span><span>战</span><span>争之后大清国从日</span><span>军铁</span><span>蹄下收回</span><span>东</span><span>北</span><span>绝</span><span>大部分</span><span>领</span><span>土的事</span><span>实</span><span>；无法解</span><span>释</span><span>北洋政府将“</span><span>二十一条</span><span>”</span><span>压缩</span><span>到</span><span>“</span><span>七条</span><span>”</span><span>的化骨</span><span>绵</span><span>掌；无法解</span><span>释</span><span>1922年的《九国公</span><span>约</span><span>》；无法解</span><span>释</span><span>蒋介石收回的</span><span>“</span><span>关税自主</span><span>权</span><span>”</span><span>。如果真的“弱国无外交”，也无法解</span><span>释</span><span>当今</span><span>世界上</span><span>诸</span><span>多小国</span><span>设</span><span>立外交部的事</span><span>实</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n如果从大</span><span>历</span><span>史的角度回</span><span>头</span><span>一看，自从</span><span>满</span><span>清政府被推翻了之后，1912－1949年</span><span>这</span><span>三十七年</span><span>间</span><span>，</span><span>孙</span><span>文、袁世</span><span>凯</span><span>、段祺瑞、黎元洪、蒋介石、</span><span>张</span><span>作霖、溥</span><span>仪</span><span>、朱毛、汪精</span><span>卫</span><span>&#8230;&#8230;</span><span>这</span><span>些人的所作所</span><span>为</span><span>，刨去了所有的外衣之后，你会</span><span>发现</span><span>他</span><span>们</span><span>所做的其</span><span>实</span><span>是同一件事：争</span><span>夺</span><span>中央政</span><span>权</span><span>。古</span><span>语</span><span>云“秦失其鹿，天下共逐之”，恰如其分。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n如果</span><span>给</span><span>你一年</span><span>时间</span><span>享尽荣</span><span>华</span><span>富</span><span>贵</span><span>，一年之后痛苦地死去。你接不接受？大多数人都不会接受。同一个</span><span>问题换</span><span>一个</span><span>问</span><span>法：如果在你出生之前</span><span>给</span><span>你</span><span>选择权</span><span>：送你一个人生，但与生俱来的是死刑</span><span>缓</span><span>期</span><span>执</span><span>行，途中有苦有</span><span>乐</span><span>，但最</span><span>终</span><span>是痛苦地死去，你要不要？我想我是不要的。但我没有</span><span>选择权</span><span>。人生</span><span>就</span><span>是一</span><span>场</span><span>悲</span><span>剧</span><span>。</span><span>佛陀在</span><span>2500<span>年前，说得对。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n一个人只有一个娘，人不可能从两个娘胎里出来。人的娘是一个具体的女人，官府不是娘，政党也不是娘，</span><span>家乡的土地也不是娘，</span><span>甚至国家也不是娘，娘是娘，官府是官府，政党是政党，</span><span>土地是土地，</span><span>国家是国家。另，人是爹</span><span>妈</span><span>辛苦</span><span>劳动挣钱</span><span>养大的，人不是官府养大的，也不是政党养大的，</span><span>也不是什么土地养大的，</span><span>甚至也不是国家养大的。</span><span>谁</span><span>生你</span><span>、</span><span>养你，要分清楚，不要乱</span><span>认</span><span>娘。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n辛亥革命的失</span><span>败</span><span>不是少数</span><span>伟</span><span>人的失</span><span>败</span><span>、也不是少数反</span><span>动</span><span>派的失</span><span>败</span><span>，而是整个民族的失</span><span>败</span><span>，</span><span>归</span><span>根</span><span>结</span><span>底是因</span><span>为</span><span>当</span><span>时这</span><span>个民族并未开化，从上到下，听不懂人</span><span>话</span><span>，只能听懂</span><span>枪</span><span>声，一群不守法的人学</span><span>习</span><span>法治国家搞共和，</span><span>东</span><span>施效</span><span>颦</span><span>，画虎不成反</span><span>类</span><span>犬，推翻清帝后，100年在原地打</span><span>转</span><span>，除了白死几千万人之外，没有什么可</span><span>观</span><span>的收益</span><span>。人的素质不进步、法治的规则不确立，搞什么都是白搭。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n世界上没有任何民族不适合搞民主，所有民族都适合搞民主，</span><span>说</span><span>中国人不适合搞民主，是假的。但各个民族的整体素</span><span>质</span><span>的确存在差异。整体素</span><span>质较</span><span>高的民族，遵</span><span>纪</span><span>守法，搞民主的成本低一些、政治</span><span>动荡</span><span>的机会低一些。整体素</span><span>质</span><span>低的民族</span><span>则</span><span>成本大一些、政治</span><span>动荡</span><span>机会大一些。民主有成本高低之分，没有适合不适合之分。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n世界</span><span>贸</span><span>易</span><span>组织</span><span>的</span><span>主要任</span><span>务</span><span>是打破关税壁</span><span>垒</span><span>，</span><span>实现</span><span>全球自由</span><span>贸</span><span>易。</span><span>贸</span><span>易壁</span><span>垒</span><span>一打破，接下来要着手打破</span><span>“</span><span>就</span><span>业</span><span>壁</span><span>垒</span><span>”</span><span>，一旦就</span><span>业</span><span>壁</span><span>垒</span><span>被打破，全球任何人可以到任何国家自由找工作、就</span><span>业</span><span>、居住、成家</span><span>立业</span><span>，</span><span>这样</span><span>就</span><span>会造成一种各国</span><span>人民</span><span>混居的状</span><span>态</span><span>，</span><span>一旦</span><span>这</span><span>种混居状</span><span>态</span><span>持</span><span>续</span><span>一百年左右，国家意</span><span>识</span><span>必然</span><span>会大大淡化，届</span><span>时</span><span>，大一</span><span>统</span><span>自然会被提上日程。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n“</span><span>汉</span><span>奸”、“亡国奴”、“</span><span>卖</span><span>国</span><span>贼</span><span>”&#8230;.</span><span>这</span><span>一</span><span>类</span><span>政治性的</span><span>话语</span><span>，是建立在以下</span><span>这</span><span>个虚</span><span>拟</span><span>的理</span><span>论</span><span>基</span><span>础</span><span>之上：“国家是人的前提，人活着是</span><span>为</span><span>了国家”。但事</span><span>实</span><span>上恰恰相反，</span><span>这</span><span>个世界上一切事物的存在，都是</span><span>为</span><span>了人的生存和幸福，“国家”</span><span>这</span><span>个事物，并不例外。一旦看透了</span><span>这</span><span>点，再看</span><span>头</span><span>重</span><span>读</span><span>近代史，豁然开朗，不言而</span><span>喻</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n有的近代史喜</span><span>欢</span><span>拿曹</span><span>锟贿选说</span><span>事。其</span><span>实</span><span>，</span><span>贿选</span><span>是一个中世</span><span>纪</span><span>半开化国家</span><span>实</span><span>施民主</span><span>宪政所</span><span>不可避免的事情。</span><span>试问</span><span>哪个</span><span>亚</span><span>洲国家</span><span>实</span><span>施民主</span><span>时</span><span>没有</span><span>发</span><span>生</span><span>过贿选</span><span>？曹</span><span>锟</span><span>是</span><span>贿选</span><span>没</span><span>错</span><span>，但他</span><span>毕</span><span>竟没有拿着</span><span>枪</span><span>逼迫</span><span>选</span><span>民</span><span>选</span><span>他吧？是</span><span>贿选</span><span>好，</span><span>还</span><span>是逼</span><span>选</span><span>好，</span><span>还</span><span>是根本没得</span><span>选</span><span>好？我</span><span>们应该</span><span>正</span><span>视贿选</span><span>。北洋</span><span>时</span><span>期出</span><span>现贿选</span><span>，并不能因此否定北洋的</span><span>进</span><span>步。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>评</span><span>价一</span><span>历</span><span>史人物不</span><span>应该</span><span>以意</span><span>识</span><span>形</span><span>态为标</span><span>准：“只要他是</span><span>爱</span><span>国的，无</span><span>论</span><span>他做了什么事、造成多大</span><span>损</span><span>失，都是</span><span>对</span><span>的”。</span><span>这</span><span>种思路是不成熟的。无</span><span>论</span><span>一个</span><span>伟</span><span>人多么</span><span>爱</span><span>国，都不能在未充分</span><span>论证</span><span>、未充分准</span><span>备</span><span>的情况下、</span><span>绑</span><span>架全民族去</span><span>贸</span><span>然救国，无</span><span>论</span><span>他的出</span><span>发</span><span>点多么高尚，都不能拿民族的命运来做</span><span>试验</span><span>，国家大事不是堆</span><span>积</span><span>木</span><span>闹</span><span>着玩</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n有人批判我：</span><span>爱</span><span>国是常</span><span>识</span><span>。可是我</span><span>认为</span><span>国家</span><span>爱</span><span>民才是常</span><span>识</span><span>。抗</span><span>战时</span><span>期</span><span>为</span><span>何涌</span><span>现</span><span>那么多</span><span>汉</span><span>奸？我</span><span>认为</span><span>深</span><span>层</span><span>次的原因，</span><span>也许</span><span>是因</span><span>为</span><span>中华民国</span><span>不</span><span>爱</span><span>民。既然国家不</span><span>爱</span><span>民，那么</span><span>对</span><span>于老百姓而言，</span><span>换</span><span>一个独裁者，并没有</span><span>实质</span><span>性的影响。所以他</span><span>们</span><span>在危急的</span><span>时</span><span>刻，把深藏于心底的算</span><span>盘</span><span>拿出来</span><span>计</span><span>算，并作出最有利</span><span>于自己</span><span>的</span><span>选择</span><span>。百姓</span><span>趋</span><span>利，</span><span>这一条，</span><span>千古不</span><span>变</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n日本人</span><span>继</span><span>承了中</span><span>华</span><span>文化的礼</span><span>仪</span><span>精</span><span>华</span><span>，</span><span>说话</span><span>温良</span><span>谦</span><span>恭，不但尽量不</span><span>说</span><span>冒犯之</span><span>语</span><span>，就算是表达异</span><span>议</span><span>，也是拐弯抹角地</span><span>讲</span><span>，</span><span>这</span><span>一切背后的精神，是</span><span>对</span><span>他人感受的在乎，<br />\n也是</span><span>对</span><span>自己人格的尊重。看当今</span><span>某些</span><span>中国人</span><span>说话</span><span>的德性，尤其是文人，言</span><span>语</span><span>之</span><span>间</span><span>尖酸刻薄，生怕</span><span>伤</span><span>人不</span><span>够</span><span>，不得不</span><span>说</span><span>：</span><span>在道德方面，</span><span>中</span><span>华</span><span>民族确</span><span>实</span><span>已</span><span>经</span><span>到了最危</span><span>险</span><span>的</span><span>时</span><span>候。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n中国近代史，如果站在独裁者、既得利益者的立</span><span>场</span><span>上看，看到的是一部外国侵略者欺</span><span>负</span><span>中</span><span>华</span><span>民族的</span><span>历</span><span>史。但是如果你站到中国</span><span>绝</span><span>大多数普通老百姓的立</span><span>场</span><span>上去看，你看到的只不</span><span>过</span><span>是外国侵略者和国内独裁者狗咬狗的一段</span><span>历</span><span>史。在</span><span>这</span><span>个狗咬狗的</span><span>过</span><span>程中，国内独裁者</span><span>绑</span><span>架了全国老百姓一起上</span><span>战场</span><span>。希望各位能看透</span><span>这</span><span>一点。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>对绝</span><span>大多数老百姓而言，生存和</span><span>发</span><span>展不但是第一主</span><span>题</span><span>，而且是永恒主</span><span>题</span><span>。所有的主</span><span>义</span><span>都是派生品（Byproduct）</span><span>。</span><span>99％的国人看近代史，</span><span>认为带领</span><span>人民打仗、</span><span>带领</span><span>人民挑起</span><span>战</span><span>争的人才是民族英雄，而我</span><span>认为</span><span>：</span><span>真正</span><span>给绝</span><span>大多数老百姓</span><span>带</span><span>来</span><span>实实</span><span>在在的利益的人</span><span>，</span><span>才是民族英雄。我</span><span>认为</span><span>我的</span><span>这</span><span>个看法（Mindset）没有</span><span>错</span><span>。永不</span><span>认错</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n我</span><span>觉</span><span>得肉食者</span><span>应该对</span><span>老百姓</span><span>讲</span><span>清楚：</span><span>夺</span><span>回</span><span>钓鱼岛</span><span>，将由</span><span>谁</span><span>去开</span><span>发</span><span>海底的石油？所得</span><span>归谁</span><span>？如何保</span><span>证</span><span>利益</span><span>输</span><span>送的透明</span><span>实</span><span>施？没</span><span>讲</span><span>清楚</span><span>这</span><span>个，再怎么</span><span>吆</span><span>喝，再怎么打起来，我都将冷眼旁</span><span>观</span><span>。</span><span>骂</span><span>我</span><span>汉</span><span>奸，我在所不辞。要我去捍</span><span>卫</span><span>一个和我切身利益无关的</span><span>东</span><span>西，等于叫我去追一个不能碰的女孩子。天下不靠</span><span>谱</span><span>之事，莫</span><span>过</span><span>于此。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>孙</span><span>中山不按法定程序（人数不</span><span>够</span><span>）召开的国会，叫“非常国会”，非常国会</span><span>选</span><span>出他当</span><span>总统</span><span>，称“非常大</span><span>总统</span><span>”。而北洋</span><span>军阀</span><span>干同等的事，</span><span>则</span><span>叫“非法国会”，</span><span>选</span><span>出的</span><span>总统</span><span>，叫“非法大</span><span>总统</span><span>”。事</span><span>实</span><span>上</span><span>孙</span><span>中山和北洋</span><span>军阀</span><span>干的事情是一</span><span>样</span><span>的：</span><span>强</span><span>奸</span><span>《</span><span>临时约</span><span>法</span><span>》</span><span>。只是因</span><span>为孙</span><span>中山是</span><span>钦</span><span>定的正面人物，“非法”才</span><span>变</span><span>成了“非常”。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n曾</span><span>经说为穷</span><span>人打天下的那帮人，</span><span>现</span><span>在</span><span>变脸</span><span>了，他</span><span>们满</span><span>大街</span><span>驱</span><span>逐</span><span>穷</span><span>人（小</span><span>贩</span><span>）。有人</span><span>说</span><span>必</span><span>须</span><span>清理小</span><span>贩</span><span>，否</span><span>则</span><span>城市会很</span><span>脏</span><span>乱。我</span><span>认为</span><span>：中国</span><span>穷</span><span>人仍然很多，</span><span>还</span><span>没到</span><span>讲</span><span>究光</span><span>鲜</span><span>的</span><span>时</span><span>候，不要打</span><span>肿脸</span><span>充胖子，</span><span>既然</span><span>是</span><span>个</span><span>穷</span><span>国</span><span>，那么</span><span>就</span><span>该脏</span><span>乱。我外公在民国</span><span>时</span><span>期就是小</span><span>贩</span><span>，就是因</span><span>为</span><span>受了国民党“城管”清理，才参加</span><span>的</span><span>游</span><span>击队</span><span>。殷</span><span>鉴</span><span>不</span><span>远</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n有人</span><span>说</span><span>：</span><span>为领导</span><span>做一百件好事，不如和</span><span>领导</span><span>一起做一件坏事。其</span><span>实</span><span>未必正确。我从</span><span>历</span><span>史中</span><span>读</span><span>出来的是：</span><span>领导</span><span>和你一起作</span><span>恶</span><span>、或者吩咐你去作</span><span>恶</span><span>，事后</span><span>为</span><span>了</span><span>杀</span><span>人</span><span>灭</span><span>口，</span><span>领导</span><span>往往会找人</span><span>灭</span><span>了你。从王竹卿到武士英，再到重</span><span>庆</span><span>王局</span><span>长</span><span>，都是如此。不要以</span><span>为</span><span>你知道</span><span>领导</span><span>的</span><span>隐</span><span>私，你就抓</span><span>住</span><span>了</span><span>领导</span><span>的把柄，其</span><span>实</span><span>你已</span><span>经处</span><span>于危</span><span>险</span><span>状</span><span>态</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n在影</span><span>视</span><span>界，判断一个</span><span>剧</span><span>本是不是悲</span><span>剧</span><span>，不是看它的</span><span>剧</span><span>情有多少</span><span>欢乐</span><span>，而是看它</span><span>结</span><span>局是否悲惨，只要</span><span>结</span><span>局是悲惨的，它就是悲</span><span>剧</span><span>。例如</span><span>红</span><span>楼梦，</span><span>历经</span><span>多少繁</span><span>华欢爱</span><span>，</span><span>结</span><span>局是悲惨的，它是悲</span><span>剧</span><span>。同理，无</span><span>论</span><span>你一生享受多少</span><span>欢乐</span><span>，你的人生都是悲</span><span>剧</span><span>，因</span><span>为结</span><span>局是悲惨的：死亡。从</span><span>这</span><span>个意</span><span>义</span><span>上看，你我的人生，都是一</span><span>场</span><span>悲</span><span>剧</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n在帝国主</span><span>义压</span><span>迫之下，北洋</span><span>时</span><span>期的中国</span><span>经济</span><span>年增</span><span>长</span><span>率几乎每年都在十个点之上，如果不内</span><span>战</span><span>，</span><span>这</span><span>个数字</span><span>还</span><span>可能更高，</span><span>这</span><span>就是所</span><span>谓</span><span>“水深火</span><span>热</span><span>”的真相。后世搞的改革开放，没有了帝国主</span><span>义</span><span>，每年</span><span>鸡</span><span>的屁增</span><span>长</span><span>也只有区区八个点。北洋</span><span>时</span><span>期搞的是真正的市</span><span>场经济</span><span>，是</span><span>彻</span><span>底的私有化，包括土地私有，是国</span><span>际</span><span>承</span><span>认</span><span>的市</span><span>场经济</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n有皇帝不代表不民主，没有皇帝也不意味着不独裁。君主可以立</span><span>宪</span><span>，共和也可以是羊</span><span>头</span><span>狗肉。关</span><span>键</span><span>不在外表和名号，而在于内容和</span><span>实质</span><span>。</span><span>读</span><span>北洋</span><span>时</span><span>期的</span><span>历</span><span>史，海峡两岸的史</span><span>书</span><span>都是不客</span><span>观</span><span>的。北洋</span><span>时</span><span>期十七年</span><span>历</span><span>史，至少基本上做到了司法独立和言</span><span>论</span><span>自由，至少</span><span>维</span><span>持了和帝国主</span><span>义</span><span>的和平，</span><span>这</span><span>是后两个政府</span><span>所</span><span>望</span><span>尘</span><span>莫及的事情。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n国民党宣</span><span>传</span><span>自己的“黄金十年”，采取</span><span>阉</span><span>割、断章的洗</span><span>脑</span><span>老路。的确，国民党黄金十年，</span><span>经济</span><span>年增</span><span>长</span><span>率有十个点左右，但是，在北洋</span><span>时</span><span>期的1912-1920年，中国的</span><span>经济</span><span>年增</span><span>长</span><span>率，</span><span>都</span><span>是在十个点以上</span><span>。</span><span>这</span><span>是“中国在帝国主</span><span>义</span><span>铁蹄</span><span>之下水深火</span><span>热</span><span>”的</span><span>论调</span><span>，所</span><span>无法自</span><span>圆</span><span>其</span><span>说</span><span>的事</span><span>实</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n通</span><span>观</span><span>北洋史，暗</span><span>杀</span><span>政治家，暴</span><span>动</span><span>，解散政党，撕</span><span>毁约</span><span>法，称帝，包</span><span>围</span><span>、解散国会，</span><span>贿选</span><span>，复辟&#8230;.</span><span>&#8230;</span><span>..凡此种种，既有南方革命党干的，也有北洋</span><span>军阀</span><span>干的，</span><span>总</span><span>之，南也好，北也</span><span>罢</span><span>，都在干同一件事情：践踏游</span><span>戏规则</span><span>。我想，北洋</span><span>宪</span><span>政失</span><span>败</span><span>的</span><span>历</span><span>史</span><span>给</span><span>我</span><span>们</span><span>的最大教</span><span>训</span><span>是：</span><span>一国</span><span>国民</span><span>如果</span><span>不养成遵守游</span><span>戏规则</span><span>的精神，是玩不好</span><span>宪</span><span>政的。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>记</span><span>得中学思想政治</span><span>课</span><span>教我：“能否制造和使用工具”，是人和禽</span><span>兽</span><span>的区</span><span>别</span><span>，</span><span>隐约记</span><span>得</span><span>还</span><span>是什么恩格斯</span><span>说</span><span>的</span><span>话</span><span>。不知道</span><span>现</span><span>在大</span><span>陆</span><span>的政治</span><span>课</span><span>本是否</span><span>还</span><span>是</span><span>这样</span><span>教育孩子</span><span>们</span><span>。我建</span><span>议</span><span>立即撤</span><span>换这</span><span>一段文字。</span><span>动</span><span>物学界有一个众所周知的事</span><span>实</span><span>：猩猩懂得将</span><span>树</span><span>枝弄滑、伸</span><span>进树</span><span>洞里、将白</span><span>蚁</span><span>引出来吃。</span><span>换</span><span>言之：猩猩也会制造和使用工具。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n所</span><span>谓</span><span>人生，是一个死刑，不</span><span>过缓</span><span>期七十年</span><span>执</span><span>行，世界是一个大大的</span><span>监狱</span><span>，人</span><span>们</span><span>在</span><span>这</span><span>所</span><span>监狱</span><span>里吃喝拉撒，偶</span><span>尔</span><span>有点开心的事，但往往又伴随着痛苦，每个人来到世界上，都在等着死刑</span><span>执</span><span>行那一天，那些所</span><span>谓</span><span>“人生多么美好”一</span><span>类话</span><span>，只能出</span><span>现</span><span>在小学生</span><span>课</span><span>文里。人生就是一</span><span>场</span><span>苦</span><span>难</span><span>。如果可以重新</span><span>选择</span><span>，我不愿降生在人世。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span>谁</span><span>声音大，</span><span>谁</span><span>就</span><span>爱</span><span>国？当年</span><span>陈</span><span>嘉庚</span><span>说</span><span>：“</span><span>敌</span><span>未出国</span><span>门</span><span>者言和即</span><span>汉</span><span>奸”，引来全国</span><span>愤</span><span>青附和。以此判断，金日成就是</span><span>个［</span><span>朝鲜</span><span>奸</span><span>］</span><span>，因</span><span>为</span><span>美</span><span>军还</span><span>没离开朝</span><span>鲜</span><span>半</span><span>岛</span><span>，金日成不</span><span>该</span><span>和美</span><span>军签</span><span>订停战协定</span><span>。胡志明</span><span>签</span><span>署日内瓦</span><span>协议</span><span>，他也是</span><span>［越南</span><span>奸</span><span>］</span><span>，因</span><span>为</span><span>法</span><span>军</span><span>当</span><span>时还</span><span>没</span><span>有</span><span>离开越南的土地。</span><span>陈</span><span>嘉庚的倡</span><span>议</span><span>，</span><span>与人</span><span>类</span><span>的</span><span>实</span><span>践</span><span>，</span><span>明</span><span>显</span><span>是</span><span>脱</span><span>节</span><span>的</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n中国国</span><span>骂</span><span>“操你</span><span>妈</span><span>”，包含两条文化信息。第一、以“操”</span><span>为</span><span>侮辱，是“以性</span><span>为</span><span>耻”的程朱理学；第二、以“</span><span>妈</span><span>”被侮辱</span><span>为</span><span>最，是孝道文化。所以，“操你</span><span>妈</span><span>”的意思，是要以天下最侮辱的</span><span>动</span><span>作、</span><span>对</span><span>待你最孝</span><span>顺</span><span>的</span><span>那个</span><span>人</span><span>。</span><span>国</span><span>骂</span><span>的含</span><span>义</span><span>，就</span><span>在于此。日本</span><span>语为</span><span>何没有“操你</span><span>妈</span><span>”？因</span><span>为</span><span>在日本，</span><span>“</span><span>性</span><span>”</span><span>并非</span><span>什么</span><span>可耻的事，所以</span><span>，也就</span><span>没</span><span>有</span><span>什么好操的。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n中国的“干爹”、“干</span><span>妈</span><span>”、“</span><span>拜把子</span><span>”文化的背后，是</span><span>传统中国社会</span><span>公共</span><span>产</span><span>品的缺位，人民缺乏安全感，所以努力</span><span>结亲</span><span>、</span><span>营</span><span>造靠山，一旦自己有</span><span>难</span><span>，干爹</span><span>、</span><span>干</span><span>妈</span><span>、</span><span>干哥</span><span>哥</span><span>来救命。</span><span>现</span><span>代的香港，医</span><span>疗</span><span>，养老，失</span><span>业</span><span>…</span><span>.</span><span>&#8230;.政府通通包</span><span>办</span><span>，平</span><span>时</span><span>缺</span><span>钱</span><span>救急，也可以</span><span>轻</span><span>松迅速</span><span>地</span><span>从</span><span>银</span><span>行</span><span>或者信贷公司</span><span>贷</span><span>到款，不需要</span><span>结亲</span><span>了，香港</span><span>的</span><span>人情味淡薄，根源就在于此。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n再怎么抵抗，</span><span>妇</span><span>女儿童都要疏散，他</span><span>们</span><span>是复</span><span>兴</span><sp